{"tid":477394,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"world of final fantasy 值唔值得玩?","createTime":"2017-11-23T04:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T06:55:36.000Z","uid":59328,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"541cc417f2f95e360d97cc76c235db1c9bdebc2f","tid":477394,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/122250_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F122250_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=959325e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來諗住隻game出係PS4到就這些機會不屬於我，點知佢犯賤到出係PC到，正又可以免費任玩了。聽個名似係超級機械人大戰D friend，係咪玩戰棋睇動話?值唔值我老翻抽時間玩?反正樂高星球大戰都就快爆機了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1e8fe32ace874bb934043701d089b6066eedb0","tid":477394,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:41:21.000Z","msg":"留個名"},{"pid":"a9ff51cc6e4dea95980bd72c04b32796eec05bad","tid":477394,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留個名</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8c97f65700c5f61aa78d1b7bfabce5a52ac3e3","tid":477394,"uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:47:14.000Z","msg":"黎緊會出電話版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cce2ac6fe14fb1384da2e716655aeee2e0f88ee","tid":477394,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊會出電話版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nscource?"},{"pid":"c91591451c3556ef65e715cc4bfe904de3526ab2","tid":47