既錢就執 好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸 超鐘意呢隻驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0496976e3922c3effe1e83c0c88737aa6aa97707","tid":477394,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢隻好玩啊 玩法好似舊個d FF既RPG玩法<br />\n而且有得捉寵 所以又有pkm feel<br />\n故事係全新 同之前FF無關係 所以唔洗驚唔識d人or劇情等等<br />\ngame入面既 角色 地方 bgm 都有取材翻以前集數既 當係比FF fans一d少彩蛋only<br />\n<br />\n始終呢隻唔係賣咩大故事同大設定 所以故事都係比較小學雞d同簡單 <br />\n都係有壞人 主角歷險識同伴去打壞人d行野故仔<br />\ngame本身既做工同畫面都唔馬乎 而且有全語音 算係有試意之作<br />\n<br />\n不過奈何睇落去唔似以往既FF 同賣都係賣係可愛風 所以就唔算太出名同大賣唔到<br />\n但係有玩過既話 比既評價都係超正面<br />\n不過可能大賣唔起 所以近排轉戰手機game黎呃埋最後既錢就執 好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸 超鐘意呢隻驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實PS4 呢D 畫面華麗向既遊戲機玩家群體點會玩呢D GAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086b2c869b2a9503b65bfa652c89dc68b7dedbf7","tid":477394,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢隻好玩啊 玩法好似舊個d FF既RPG玩法<br />\n而且有得捉寵 所以又有pkm feel<br />\n故事係全新 同之前FF無關係 所以唔洗驚唔識d人or劇情等等<br />\ngame入面既 角色 地方 bgm 都有取材翻以前集數既 當係比FF fans一d少彩蛋only<br />\n<br />\n始終呢隻唔係賣咩大故事同大設定 所以故事都係比較小學雞d同簡單 <br />\n都係有壞人 主角歷險識同伴去打壞人d行野故仔<br />\ngame本身既做工同畫面都唔馬乎 而且有全語音 算係有試意之作<br />\n<br />\n不過奈何睇落去唔似以往既FF 同賣都係賣係可愛風 所以就唔算太出名同大賣唔到<br />\n但係有玩過既話 比既評價都係超正面<br />\n不過可能大賣唔起 所以近排轉戰手機game黎呃埋最後既錢就執 好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸 超鐘意呢隻驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實PS4 呢D 畫面華麗向既遊戲機玩家群體點會玩呢D GAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係架 但係呢隻驚我個人覺得真係值回票價既作品<br />\n跑出唔到 真係好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9963378cf0f2de2b6fcc9c97e4ade2e9a173c85f","tid":477394,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:11:54.000Z","msg":"FF15講左會出Pc<br />\n然後都會出手機板 手機板啲人會變左二頭身<br />\n想知利維坦會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdaeb3b6092181b768e201247d11a2fdb90435c0","tid":477394,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>FF15講左會出Pc<br />\n然後都會出手機板 手機板啲人會變左二頭身<br />\n想知利維坦會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RSYtV3hQyWk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRSYtV3hQyWk&d=qZPSKHKmrXV2l37FClLyksn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=2166a1d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RSYtV3hQyWk</a><br />\n轉左條蟲仔囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19b755f0bbd258d69d22a932b8a2d52109f8399","tid":477394,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢隻好玩啊 玩法好似舊個d FF既RPG玩法<br />\n而且有得捉寵 所以又有pkm feel<br />\n故事係全新 同之前FF無關係 所以唔洗驚唔識d人or劇情等等<br />\ngame入面既 角色 地方 bgm 都有取材翻以前集數既 當係比FF fans一d少彩蛋only<br />\n<br />\n始終呢隻唔係賣咩大故事同大設定 所以故事都係比較小學雞d同簡單 <br />\n都係有壞人 主角歷險識同伴去打壞人d行野故仔<br />\ngame本身既做工同畫面都唔馬乎 而且有全語音 算係有試意之作<br />\n<br />\n不過奈何睇落去唔似以往既FF 同賣都係賣係可愛風 所以就唔算太出名同大賣唔到<br />\n但係有玩過既話 比既評價都係超正面<br />\n不過可能大賣唔起 所以近排轉戰手機game黎呃埋最後既錢就執 好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸 超鐘意呢隻驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實PS4 呢D 畫面華麗向既遊戲機玩家群體點會玩呢D GAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係架 但係呢隻驚我個人覺得真係值回票價既作品<br />\n跑出唔到 真係好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBTW~~佢啱啱出果隻大DQ X FF 大富翁好似都唔多賣得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c41f8aca7b2c191f94d2ac647440082e92ba46","tid":477394,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:21:47.000Z","msg":"果陣玩體驗版見到d人仔大頭身細心諗做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5862378f35eaf5dbfe416db657705601a4ad5ec","tid":477394,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢隻好玩啊 玩法好似舊個d FF既RPG玩法<br />\n而且有得捉寵 所以又有pkm feel<br />\n故事係全新 同之前FF無關係 所以唔洗驚唔識d人or劇情等等<br />\ngame入面既 角色 地方 bgm 都有取材翻以前集數既 當係比FF fans一d少彩蛋only<br />\n<br />\n始終呢隻唔係賣咩大故事同大設定 所以故事都係比較小學雞d同簡單 <br />\n都係有壞人 主角歷險識同伴去打壞人d行野故仔<br />\ngame本身既做工同畫面都唔馬乎 而且有全語音 算係有試意之作<br />\n<br />\n不過奈何睇落去唔似以往既FF 同賣都係賣係可愛風 所